#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 7. Ānāpānavagga → ānāpānādipeyyālo (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.57:0.2"
msgid "7. Ānāpānavagga"
msgstr "7. Breathing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 57. Aṭṭhikamahapphalasutta → aṭṭhikasuttaṃ (bj) | aṭṭhika mahapphala-mahānisaṃsā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.57:0.3"
msgid "57. Aṭṭhikamahapphalasutta"
msgstr "57. A Skeleton"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.129"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.57:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn46.57:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhikasaññā, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when the perception of a skeleton is developed and cultivated "
"it’s very fruitful and beneficial."

msgctxt "sn46.57:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, aṭṭhikasaññā kathaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā?"
msgstr "How so?"

msgctxt "sn46.57:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aṭṭhikasaññāsahagataṃ satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … "
"aṭṭhikasaññāsahagataṃ upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ "
"virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the perception of a skeleton together with "
"the awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity, which rely on seclusion, "
"fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go."

msgctxt "sn46.57:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhikasaññā evaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how the perception of a skeleton, when developed and cultivated, is "
"very fruitful and beneficial.”"

#. <h2>
msgctxt "sn46.57:1.6"
msgid "Aññataraphalasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="ms" id="p_14S5_666"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.57:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhikasaññāya, bhikkhave, bhāvitāya bahulīkatāya dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ "
"aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese "
"anāgāmitā. "
msgstr ""
"“When the perception of a skeleton is developed and cultivated you can "
"expect one of two results: enlightenment in the present life, or if there’s "
"something left over, non-return."

msgctxt "sn46.57:2.2"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitāya ca kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhikasaññāya kathaṃ bahulīkatāya "
"dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā "
"upādisese anāgāmitā? "
msgstr "How so? ...\""

msgctxt "sn46.57:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu aṭṭhikasaññāsahagataṃ satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … "
"pe … aṭṭhikasaññāsahagataṃ upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ "
"virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn46.57:2.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitāya kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhikasaññāya evaṃ bahulīkatāya dvinnaṃ "
"phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā "
"upādisese anāgāmitā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "sn46.57:2.5"
msgid "Mahatthasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h2><p>
